OL,3,CDonald Trump lands in China ahead of
OL,4,Cpivotal meeting with Xi Jinping
OL,6,FDonald Trump arrived in Beijing on
OL,7,FWednesday for his hotly anticipated
OL,8,Ftalks with Chinese President Xi
OL,9,FJinping on the Iran war, trade and
OL,10,FTaiwan.
OL,12,FThe meat of the summit doesn't start
OL,13,Funtil Thursday, when the leaders hold
OL,14,Fbilateral talks, visit the Temple of
OL,15,FHeaven, where Chinese emperors once
OL,16,Fprayed for bumper crops, and take part
OL,17,Fin a formal banquet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
