OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778702756
OL,3,CDonald Trump lands in China ahead of
OL,4,Cpivotal meeting with Xi Jinping
OL,6,FBut the Chinese offered Trump a pomp-
OL,7,Ffilled welcome, literally rolling out
OL,8,Fthe red carpet for him after Air Force
OL,9,FOne landed in Beijing.
OL,11,FThe president was greeted by Chinese
OL,12,FVice President Han Zheng as he touched
OL,13,Fdown to waving crowds.
OL,15,FThe welcoming ceremony included a
OL,16,Fmilitary honour guard, a military band
OL,17,Fand some 300 people waving Chinese and
OL,18,FAmerican flags and chanting, "Welcome,
OL,19,Fwelcome! Warm welcome!" as Trump made
OL,20,Fhis way to his waiting limousine.
