OL,3,CDonald Trump lands in China ahead of
OL,4,Cpivotal meeting with Xi Jinping
OL,6,F"We're the two superpowers," Trump
OL,7,Ftold reporters as he departed the
OL,8,FWhite House on Tuesday for the long
OL,9,Fflight to Beijing. "We're the
OL,10,Fstrongest nation on Earth in terms of
OL,11,Fmilitary. China's considered second."
